#: .\power_up\templates\power_up\about.html:10 .\power_up\views.py:33
msgid "About Power-Up"
msgstr "Über Power-Up"

#: .\power_up\templates\power_up\about.html:13
#| msgid ""
#| "We're a Luxembourg-based company building digital platforms thatmatter."
msgid ""
"We're a Luxembourg-based company building digital platforms that matter."
msgstr ""
"Wir sind ein in Luxemburg ansässiges Unternehmen, das digitale Plattformen "
"mit Bedeutung entwickelt."

#: .\power_up\templates\power_up\about.html:25
#| msgid "Our Platforms"
msgid "Our Story"
msgstr "Unsere Geschichte"

#: .\power_up\templates\power_up\about.html:29
#| msgid ""
#| "Power-Up was founded with a simple belief: Luxembourg deservesworld-class "
#| "digital platforms designed for its unique community."
msgid ""
"Power-Up was founded with a simple belief: Luxembourg deserves world-class "
"digital platforms designed for its unique community."
msgstr ""
"Power-Up wurde mit einer einfachen Überzeugung gegründet: Luxemburg verdient"
" erstklassige digitale Plattformen, die für seine einzigartige Gemeinschaft "
"entwickelt wurden."

#: .\power_up\templates\power_up\about.html:32
#| msgid ""
#| "In a country where everyone seems to know everyone, we recognized theneed "
#| "for platforms that respect privacy while fostering genuineconnections. "
#| "Whether it's dating, wine appreciation, or professionalnetworking, we build "
#| "with Luxembourg's values at heart."
msgid ""
"In a country where everyone seems to know everyone, we recognized the need "
"for platforms that respect privacy while fostering genuine connections. "
"Whether it's dating, wine appreciation, or professional networking, we build"
" with Luxembourg's values at heart."
msgstr ""
"In einem Land, in dem scheinbar jeder jeden kennt, haben wir den Bedarf an "
"Plattformen erkannt, die die Privatsphäre respektieren und zugleich echte "
"Verbindungen fördern. Ob Dating, Weingenuss oder berufliches Netzwerken – "
"wir entwickeln mit den Werten Luxemburgs im Herzen."

#: .\power_up\templates\power_up\about.html:35
#| msgid ""
#| "Today, our platforms serve thousands of users across Luxembourg andthe "
#| "Greater Region, and we're just getting started."
msgid ""
"Today, our platforms serve thousands of users across Luxembourg and the "
"Greater Region, and we're just getting started."
msgstr ""
"Heute bedienen unsere Plattformen Tausende von Nutzern in ganz Luxemburg und"
" der Großregion – und wir stehen erst am Anfang."

#: .\power_up\templates\power_up\about.html:43
msgid "Live Platforms"
msgstr "Live-Plattformen"

#: .\power_up\templates\power_up\about.html:47
msgid "Founded"
msgstr "Gegründet"

#: .\power_up\templates\power_up\about.html:51
msgid "Based in Luxembourg"
msgstr "Mit Sitz in Luxemburg"

#: .\power_up\templates\power_up\about.html:64
msgid "Our Values"
msgstr "Unsere Werte"

#: .\power_up\templates\power_up\about.html:67
msgid "The principles that guide everything we build."
msgstr "Die Prinzipien, die alles leiten, was wir bauen."

#: .\power_up\templates\power_up\about.html:79
msgid "Privacy by Design"
msgstr "Privatsphäre by Design"

#: .\power_up\templates\power_up\about.html:81
#| msgid ""
#| "In Luxembourg's close-knit community, privacy isn't optional. Webuild data "
#| "protection into the foundation of every platform, givingusers control over "
#| "their information."
msgid ""
"In Luxembourg's close-knit community, privacy isn't optional. We build data "
"protection into the foundation of every platform, giving users control over "
"their information."
msgstr ""
"In der eng verbundenen Gemeinschaft Luxemburgs ist Privatsphäre nicht "
"optional. Wir verankern den Datenschutz im Fundament jeder Plattform und "
"geben den Nutzern die Kontrolle über ihre Daten."

#: .\power_up\templates\power_up\about.html:92
msgid "Human Connection"
msgstr "Menschliche Verbindung"

#: .\power_up\templates\power_up\about.html:94
#| msgid ""
#| "Technology should bring people together, not replace humaninteraction. Our "
#| "platforms facilitate real connections - whetherromantic, professional, or "
#| "experiential."
msgid ""
"Technology should bring people together, not replace human interaction. Our "
"platforms facilitate real connections - whether romantic, professional, or "
"experiential."
msgstr ""
"Technologie sollte Menschen zusammenbringen, nicht die menschliche "
"Interaktion ersetzen. Unsere Plattformen ermöglichen echte Verbindungen – ob"
" romantisch, beruflich oder erlebnisorientiert."

#: .\power_up\templates\power_up\about.html:105
msgid "Local Focus"
msgstr "Lokaler Fokus"

#: .\power_up\templates\power_up\about.html:107
#| msgid ""
#| "We understand Luxembourg's unique multilingual, multiculturalcontext. Our "
#| "platforms are designed specifically for this community,not adapted from "
#| "solutions built elsewhere."
msgid ""
"We understand Luxembourg's unique multilingual, multicultural context. Our "
"platforms are designed specifically for this community, not adapted from "
"solutions built elsewhere."
msgstr ""
